<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tribhu</hi> vanaccakkaravarttikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>vikkiramacoḻa<hi rend="grantha">de</hi> varkku yāṇṭu 7 Āvatu I<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>panāyaṟṟu nālānāḷāṉa koṭṭunāḷ <hi rend="grantha">3</hi>
<lb n="2" break="no"/><num value="19"><g type="numeral">10</g> 9</num> ṉāl cuttamalivaḷanāṭṭu taniyūr <hi rend="grantha">śrīrājādhirāja</hi> ccaruppetimaṅkalattu Eṭṭāñceri piṟāntūr karuṇākara<hi rend="grantha">bha</hi> ṭṭaṉ <hi rend="grantha">brāhma</hi>ṇi
<lb n="3"/>Āṇṭa naṅkaiccāniyum Ivaḷ makaḷ cattiyapāvaiyum Uṭaiyār tiruviṭaimarutuṭaiyārkku cantiviḷakku Iraṇṭu Erikka <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>paṇṭārattu Oṭukkiṉa kācu 2 Ikkācu Iraṇṭiṉ <unclear>palic</unclear>ai koṇṭu canti viḷakku Iraṇ<unclear>ṭum ca</unclear>ntirātittaval Erikka Itu pa(ṇ)<hi rend="grantha">nmā</hi>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ye<hi rend="grantha">śvara raṣai</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Ivai koyilkaṇakku ma<unclear>ru</unclear>tu<unclear>ṭai</unclear>yāṉ Eḻuttu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

